MiiKeyFocusTraversalGroup
public class MiKeyFocusTraversalGroupList
extends MiParts
implements MiiKeyFocusTraversalGroup

This class implements a MiiKeyFocusTraversalGroup as a list of parts that are to receive keyboard/enter-key focus. Use the methods of the super class MiParts to add and remove parts from this tab group.
